  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The current study seeks to begin the crucial work of creating effective protocols to prevent
      opioid misuse, addiction, and related complications by developing and pilot testing an opioid
      risk screening protocol at Wisconsin trauma centers.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <overall_status>Recruiting</overall_status>
